    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Violence and intimidation by revolutionaries seeking to modify the existing sociopolitical structure, but not to overthrow an existing regime.  Examples include some animal-rights campaigns and the ANC's campaign to end apartheid in South Africa.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
